title: Take That’s Howard Donald forced to miss Gala night of Gary Barlow’s The Girls Musical after his wife goes into labour
text:
TV Magazine GREATEST DAY Take That’s Howard Donald forced to miss Gala night of Gary Barlow’s The Girls Musical after his wife goes into labour 
The singer’s new arrival may mean that his appearance on the Let It Shine final this weekend is cancelled Exclusive By ANDY HALLS, TV Editor 21st February 2017, 12:13 pm
